{"id":17937,"date":"2022-12-31T04:19:47","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:19:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:19:47","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:19:47","slug":"piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Piaggio Beverly S gi\u00e1 235 tri\u1ec7u ra m\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch Vi\u1ec7t"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<p>M\u1eabu xe tay ga 400 ph\u00e2n kh\u1ed1i nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u t\u1eeb \u00dd, trang b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Ng\u00e0y 22\/11, h\u00e3ng xe m\u00e1y \u00dd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1eabu xe c\u00f4n tay Beverly S 400 HPE.  M\u1eabu xe tay ga c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng Italy.  Beverly S h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u00edch tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111am m\u00ea th\u1ec3 thao.  \u1ede ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe ga kho\u1ea3ng 400 cc t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HPE Beverly S 400 s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Honda SH 350i, Yamaha Xmax 300, BMW C 400 GT, Yamaha Tmax.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"680x0\" alt=\"Piaggio Beverly S 400 HPE ra m\u1eaft H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ng\u00e0y 22\/11. \u1ea2nh: L\u01b0\u01a1ng D\u0169ng\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" title=\"piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg 680w\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Image\">Piaggio Beverly S 400 HPE ra m\u1eaft H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ng\u00e0y 22\/11. \u1ea2nh: L\u01b0\u01a1ng D\u0169ng<\/p>\n<p>  <img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441084_957_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"Piaggio ra m\u1eaft Beverly S 400 HPE t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ng\u00e0y 22\/11.\" title=\"1672441084_957_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441084_95_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"Beverly S 400 HPE nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng Italy, gi\u00e1 235 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.\" title=\"1672441084_95_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441084_22_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"M\u1eabu xe ga th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Italy h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u00edch tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111am m\u00ea th\u1ec3 thao.\" title=\"1672441084_22_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441085_53_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"Xe trang b\u1ecb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng LED. \u0110\u1ea7u xe l\u1eafp k\u00ednh ch\u1eafn gi\u00f3.\" title=\"1672441085_53_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441085_21_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 LCD 5,5 inch hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin xe, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh.\" title=\"1672441085_21_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441085_265_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"B\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eafp v\u00e0nh 16 inch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf 7 ch\u1ea5u k\u00e9p.\" title=\"1672441085_265_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441085_516_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"H\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u1ed5ng s\u1ea1c USB. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kh\u00f3a th\u00f4ng minh.\" title=\"1672441085_516_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441085_155_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ecnh x\u0103ng \u1edf s\u00e0n xe, dung t\u00edch 12 l\u00edt.\" title=\"1672441085_155_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441085_116_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"Y\u00ean xe ph\u00e2n t\u1ea7ng phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ec3 thao.\" title=\"1672441085_116_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441085_389_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"\u0110\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 HPE 400 ph\u00e2n kh\u1ed1i, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 35,3 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c.\" title=\"1672441085_389_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441085_762_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"C\u1ee5m \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu LED thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o.\" title=\"1672441085_762_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><img decoding=\"async\" data-w=\"\" data-h=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672441085_354_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet.jpg\" data-component-caption=\"H\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed3 d\u01b0\u1edbi y\u00ean dung t\u00edch l\u1edbn, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9a hai m\u0169 b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m 3\/4 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng ti\u1ec7n d\u1ee5ng.\" title=\"1672441085_354_piaggio-beverly-s-gia-235-trieu-ra-mat-khach-viet\"><\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Piaggio \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb Beverly S l\u00e0 xe ga b\u00e1nh l\u1edbn, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u00e1c m\u1eabu Liberty v\u00e0 Medley.  Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Beverly S l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u m\u00f4t\u00f4 \u00dd.  Beverly S \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e8n LED, k\u00ednh ch\u1eafn gi\u00f3, y\u00ean xe ph\u00e2n t\u1ea7ng th\u1ec3 thao, \u1ed1ng x\u1ea3 k\u00e9p.  C\u1eb7p m\u00e2m \u0111\u00fac thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf 7 ch\u1ea5u k\u00e9p, v\u1edbi v\u00e0nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc 16 inch v\u00e0 v\u00e0nh sau 14 inch.  C\u1ee5m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 LCD 5,5 inch, hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 xe v\u00e0 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Beverly S \u0111\u1eadm ch\u1ea5t th\u1ec3 thao v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1eaft g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n.  V\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00ecnh x\u0103ng n\u1eb1m ch\u00ednh gi\u1eefa g\u00e1c ch\u00e2n.  H\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed3 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u1ed5ng s\u1ea1c USB.  H\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed3 d\u01b0\u1edbi y\u00ean dung t\u00edch l\u1edbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 m\u0169 b\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m 3\/4 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb th\u00eam \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Beverly S 400 HPE (High Performance Engine) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 xi-lanh \u0111\u01a1n, dung t\u00edch 400 cc, l\u00e0m m\u00e1t b\u1eb1ng dung d\u1ecbch, phun x\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 35,3 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i 7.500 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat.  M\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i 37,7 Nm t\u1ea1i 5.500 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat.  M\u1ee9c ti\u00eau hao nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u 3,7 l\u00edt\/100 km \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p, theo c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Beverly S d\u00e0i 2.155 mm, r\u1ed9ng 800 mm v\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf 1.550 mm.  K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi Honda SH 350i v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i 2.160 mm, r\u1ed9ng 743 mm v\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i c\u01a1 s\u1edf 1.450 mm.  M\u1eabu xe tay ga c\u1ee7a Piaggio n\u1eb7ng 195 kg, dung t\u00edch b\u00ecnh x\u0103ng 12 l\u00edt.  Trang b\u1ecb an to\u00e0n v\u1edbi phanh \u0111\u0129a \u0111\u01a1n tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e1nh, \u0111\u0129a tr\u01b0\u1edbc 300 mm, \u0111\u0129a sau 240 mm, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3 c\u1ee9ng phanh ABS hai k\u00eanh.  Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ch\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1ee3t ASR, c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eang.  H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng kh\u00f3a th\u00f4ng minh.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\">Piaggio Beverly S 400 HPE gi\u00e1 235 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng, 4 m\u00e0u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.  C\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe nh\u01b0 Honda SH 350i l\u1eafp r\u00e1p gi\u00e1 149 tri\u1ec7u, Yamaha XMAX 300 (nh\u1eadp Indonesia) gi\u00e1 129 tri\u1ec7u, BMW C 400 GT (nh\u1eadp) gi\u00e1 349 tri\u1ec7u v\u00e0 Yamaha TMAX (nh\u1eadp Nh\u1eadt) gi\u00e1 409 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Minh V\u0169<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1eabu xe tay ga 400 ph\u00e2n kh\u1ed1i nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u t\u1eeb \u00dd, trang b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh n\u0103ng, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7. Ng\u00e0y 22\/11, h\u00e3ng xe m\u00e1y \u00dd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u t\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1eabu xe c\u00f4n tay Beverly S 400 HPE. M\u1eabu xe tay ga c\u1ee1 l\u1edbn nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng Italy. Beverly S h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16219,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17937"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17937"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17937\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16219"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17937"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17937